WEBVTT

00:03:29.300 --> 00:03:31.195
Chigirtkalar qisqichbaqalarga
o'xshaydi.

00:03:31.219 --> 00:03:34.864
Kriketlarda, ba'zi odamlar aytadiki, 
popkorn xushbo'yligi bor.

00:03:34.888 --> 00:03:38.587
Hasharotlarni oziq-ovqat uchun
yetishtirish, shuningdek, chorvachilik

00:03:38.611 --> 00:03:40.365
fermalariga qaraganda kamroq

00:03:40.389 --> 00:03:43.361
ekologik ta'sirga ega, chunki 
hasharotlar juda kam issiqxona

00:03:43.385 --> 00:03:46.288
gazini chiqaradi va kam joy,
suv va oziq-ovqat sarflaydi.

00:03:46.312 --> 00:03:48.511
Ijtimoiy-iqtisodiy tomondan,
hasharot ta'minoti

00:03:48.535 --> 00:03:50.641
rivojlanayotgan davlatlardagi odamlarni

00:03:50.665 --> 00:03:53.099
rivojlantirishi mumkin,
chunki hasharot fermalari

00:03:53.123 --> 00:03:57.049
kichik hajmli, yuqori mahsuldor va saqlash
uchun arzon bo'lishi ham mumkin.

00:03:57.073 --> 00:04:00.529
Hasharotlarni chorva mollari 
uchun barqaror oziq-ovqat mahsulotlariga